# Backup Validator IP Whitelist Configuration
# 
# This file defines IP addresses and networks that are allowed to connect to the Backup Validator service.
# Each line should contain a single IP address or network in CIDR notation.
# Lines starting with # are treated as comments.

# Allow localhost
127.0.0.1
::1

# Allow private networks 
10.0.0.0/8      # Class A private network
172.16.0.0/12   # Class B private network
192.168.0.0/16  # Class C private network

# Examples of specific hosts and networks - uncomment and modify as needed
# 192.168.1.10    # Specific host
# 192.168.5.0/24  # Specific subnet 